        <updateDate>2008-07-15T20:47:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Ludlow Massacre National Historic Landmark Act - Designates the Ludlow Tent Colony Site (a site where striking miners and their families lived during the 1913-1914 Colorado coal strike) in Las Animas County, Colorado, as the &quot;Ludlow Massacre National Historic Landmark.&quot; </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
